{"tid":1365673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727口號 掃黑除惡 掃黑除惡 掃黑除惡","createTime":"2019-07-25T17:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T17:52:39.000Z","uid":43556,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6799908a7e69056901362e10bf42d730b7961a41","tid":1365673,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"聽到網台朱凱廸話要印<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">掃黑除惡</span></strong></span> 呢句BANNER<br />\n<br />\n因為大陸網民會翻牆睇香港媒體<br />\n我強烈建議 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">掃黑除惡</span></strong></span> 成為727主要口號，掃黑除惡係中共現時主要工作，大陸網民一定會支持香港同胞推動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">掃黑除惡</span></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n咩係掃黑除惡?<br />\n<br />\n中共中央、國務院早前發出《關於開展掃黑除惡專項鬥爭的通知》，決定在全國開展掃黑除惡專項鬥爭。而在較早前的中共十九屆中央紀委二次全會中，中共總書記習近平強調，要把掃黑除惡同反腐敗結合起來，既抓涉黑組織，也抓後面的「保護傘」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/158235/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%A4%A7%E5%8A%9B-%E6%8E%83%E9%BB%91%E9%99%A4%E6%83%A1-%E6%98%8E%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%A98%E9%A1%9E%E9%BB%91%E6%83%A1%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F158235%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%258E%2583%25E9%25BB%2591%25E9%2599%25A4%25E6%2583%25A1-%25E6%2598%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%25BE%25A98%25E9%25A1%259E%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%2583%25A1%25E5%258B%25A2%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25B1%25A1&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=6d62ed63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/158235/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%A4%A7%E5%8A%9B-%E6%8E%83%E9%BB%91%E9%99%A4%E6%83%A1-%E6%98%8E%E7%A2%BA%E5%AE%9A%E7%BE%A98%E9%A1%9E%E9%BB%91%E6%83%A1%E5%8B%A2%E5%8A%9B%E5%B0%8D%E8%B1%A1</a>"},{"pid":"d182ee1b59cebfa43df70d751219ab5d73f05d0f","tid":1365673,"uid":43556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy